Synopsis:
   away [away message]

Description:
   Basically this commands sets you away.  Additionally - if configured so -
   it will show the away message on all channels you are on, change your
   nick to something else (e.g. john_away) while you are away, or start
   logging messages and notices to a log file.

Aliases:
   setaway

See Also:
   back(9); readlog(9); remlog(9); away(1)

